          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve billing periods from a database. It allows for filtering based on a specific billing period or retrieving only current billing periods. The procedure logs its execution details, including any exceptions, to an application log."
